Harden
Discworld ritual help
Harden

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Telltale Heart - Slows the beating of anothers' heart to nothing.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This is an offensive ritual that cuts off another's blood flow and responds
with a corresponding quickening of your own.  This is not the safest of
prospects, as it is capable of causing internal damage.
.EP
